channel.title: TFS 2010 Teamprise integration demonstrated at PDC 2008
channel.description: During Brian Harry's "Team Foundation Server 2010 Cool New Features" presentation at PDC, he demonstrated Teamprise working with TFS 2010 (codenamed "Rosario").  Not often you get one of the most senior technical people in Microsoft using Eclipse on stage...
channel.dc:creator: Martin
